      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_7_12474-12556",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "12474-12556",
      "markText": "“奇诺，这颗珍珠是邪恶的。趁它没把我们毁掉以前，我们把它毁了吧。我们用两块石头把它压碎吧。我们把它扔回到海里去吧，它本来是属于海的。奇诺，它是邪恶的，它是邪恶的！”",
      "totalCount": 728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12474&rangeEnd=12556",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12474&rangeEnd=12556"
