    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_7_10358-10441",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10358-10441",
      "markText": "“我们的确知道我们从出世一直到进棺材都在受骗，连棺材他们也要敲竹杠。但是我们还是活下来了。你反抗的不是那些收买珍珠的人，而是整个制度，整个生活方式，因此我替你担心。”",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10358&rangeEnd=10441",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10358&rangeEnd=10441"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_4_2253-2298",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2253-2298",
      "markText": "黎明很快地来到了，一抹淡彩，一道红光，一片明亮，然后爆发出一团烈火——太阳从海湾里升起了。",
      "totalCount": 416,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2253&rangeEnd=2298",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2253&rangeEnd=2298"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_4_5724-5758",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5724-5758",
      "markText": "黄澄澄的太阳把他们的黑影子投在他们面前，因此他们在自己的影子上走着。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5724&rangeEnd=5758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5724&rangeEnd=5758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_5_2924-3023",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2924-3023",
      "markText": "这些珠母会碰到一点意外，一粒沙子会陷在肌肉的皱褶里，刺激肌肉，直到肌肉出于自卫用一层光滑的珍珠质把沙粒裹住。这情况一旦开始，肌肉就继续包裹那外来物，直到它在浪潮的冲击中掉出来，或者直到那珠母被毁灭。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2924&rangeEnd=3023",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2924&rangeEnd=3023"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_8_1396-1473",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1396-1473",
      "markText": "正当她举起胳臂要扔的时候，他扑到了她的身上，抓住她的胳臂，把珍珠从她手里夺下。他用握紧的拳头朝她脸上揍了一拳，她便跌倒在圆石块当中，他又朝她的腰踢了一脚。",
      "totalCount": 377,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1396&rangeEnd=1473",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1396&rangeEnd=1473"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_8_3939-3989",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3939-3989",
      "markText": "他没有想到去动用一只邻居的小船。这个念头一次也没有在他脑子里出现，正如他决不可能想到破坏一只船一样。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3939&rangeEnd=3989",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3939&rangeEnd=3989"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_9_7863-7962",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "7863-7962",
      "markText": "于是，他看到她的脸，要在那里找到软弱的表情，找到害怕或者犹豫的表情，而她脸上都没有。她的眼睛非常明亮。于是他无可奈何地耸耸肩，但他却从她那里得到了力量。当他们继续前进的时候，那就不再是惊惶的奔逃了。",
      "totalCount": 357,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7863&rangeEnd=7962",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7863&rangeEnd=7962"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101444_5_2490-2549",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2490-2549",
      "markText": "她没有直接为孩子的复元祈祷——她祈祷让他们采到一颗珍珠来请大夫给孩子医治，因为人们的脑子像海湾里的海市蜃楼一样的虚幻。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101444&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2490&rangeEnd=2549",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/70432e80813ab8e20g014ad1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2490&rangeEnd=2549"
